managedappdistributiond(8)  System Manager's Manual managedappdistributiond(8)

NAME
     managedappdistributiond – macOS managed app distribution daemon

DESCRIPTION
     managedappdistributiond is used by the system during managed app
     installation. It should not be invoked manually.

